---
import { ContactForm } from "../contact-form";
import SectionHeader from "../SectionHeader.astro";
---

<section
  id="contact"
  class="bg-cosmic-latte-dark py-24 scroll-mt-24 md:scroll-mt-15"
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <SectionHeader title="Contact" />
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-ink-light leading-relaxed">
          プロジェクトのご相談やお問い合わせは、フォームまたは下記の連絡先からお気軽にどうぞ。
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">
              メールアドレス
            </h3>
            <a
              href="mailto:contact@ryosuz.com"
              class="text-ink hover:text-ink-light transition-colors"
            >
              contact@ryosuz.com
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm text-ink-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">
              ソーシャル
            </h3>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a
                href="https://github.com"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-ink hover:text-ink-light transition-colors"
              >
                GitHub
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://twitter.com"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-ink hover:text-ink-light transition-colors"
              >
                X (Twitter)
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <ContactForm client:visible />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
